<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53001594/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """Two deliveries will be published at the beginning of the course. They are compulsory and non-recoverable. They account for 60% of the final grade, and will be considered both in the ordinary and extraordinary calls.
1.-Ordinary call:
1.1.- Written exam: 40% of the final grade
1.2.- Deliveries: 60% of the final grade

2.- Extraordinary call:
2.1.- Written exam: 40% of the final grade
2.2.- Deliveries: 60% of the final grade"""@es ;
